that means we have to rewrite it.

97
00:07:02,214 --> 00:07:03,215
Seriously.

98
00:07:06,051 --> 00:07:07,219
"Change the title."

99
00:07:07,302 --> 00:07:09,513
"Produced by Haha Jungho
Fisheries Distribution."

100
