It's so lame.

101
00:07:11,014 --> 00:07:12,975
"Check for action details."

102
00:07:13,058 --> 00:07:14,268
"Reexamine the time period."

103
00:07:14,351 --> 00:07:16,353
"Lack of probability
in the lead character's behavior

104
00:07:16,436 --> 00:07:18,897
