00:30:34,083 --> 00:30:37,670
-Good work.
-Gosh, I loved your eyes.

488
00:30:37,753 --> 00:30:40,631
Oh, Mary Yoo. Great job.

489
00:30:40,714 --> 00:30:42,633
-I loved it.
-Thank you.

490
00:30:43,467 --> 00:30:45,803
-This is for you, Mr. Ha.
